### L6-003：16类基础服务能力矩阵

#### 第一梯队 — 必须建设

**A. UAM — 用户与账户服务
能力
Account register/login/session Token/SSO/MFA/third-party OAuth/device fingerprint

**B. PAY — 支付与交易服务
能力
WeChat Pay/Alipay/UnionPay QuickPass/Digital RMB/PayPal/Stripe

**C. SMS — 安全与合规服务
能力
MFA/RBAC permission management/fraud detection/audit logs/PCI-DSS compliance

**D. CFG — 配置与开关服务
能力
Multi-environment config/namespace isolation/version management/gradual release/realtime push/sensitive encryption

#### 第二梯队 — 尽快建设

**E. NTF — 消息通知服务
能力
SMS/email/app push/in-app message/template management/rate control/smart routing

**F. DAT — 数据采集服务
能力
Frontend SDK/backend SDK/app SDK/event model/data validation/realtime monitoring

**G. MED — 媒体处理服务
能力
Resumable upload/image processing (thumbnail/watermark/format conversion)/video transcoding/storage

**H. MKT — 营销优惠服务
能力
Coupons/quantity discounts/discounts/stacking calculation/budget control/inventory management/campaign management

**I. PIM — 积分会员服务
能力
Points account/points earning/points redemption/membership level/growth value/points mall

#### 第三梯队 — 按需建设

**J. MOD — 内容审核服务
能力
Text moderation/image moderation/video moderation/prohibited content detection/precision/recall modes

**K. GMG — 用户增长服务
能力
Invite code/fission/team purchase/task system/A/B testing/anti-fraud risk control

**L. CSC — 客服工单服务
能力
Ticket create/process/close/rate/FAQ Q&A/knowledge base/data analysis

**M. SRS — 搜索推荐服务
能力
Full-text search/semantic search/highlight/correction/personalized recommendation/collaborative filtering

**N. CDN — 内容分发服务
能力
Global acceleration/HTTPS/anti-hotlink/cache strategy/performance optimization

#### 第四梯队 — 长期规划

**O. INS — 分析洞察服务
能力
Funnel analysis/retention analysis/path analysis/attribution analysis/user profiling/report dashboard

**P. STR — 实时计算服务
能力
Real-time ETL/real-time metrics/real-time risk control/unified stream-batch/Flink

**Q. OPS — 运营效率服务
能力
Message center/popup management/banner management/CMS content management/form system

### L6-004：基础服务依赖关系矩阵

| 被依赖\依赖
|----------------------------------------|-----|-----|-----|-----|-----|-----|-----|-----|
| UAM (用户账户
| PAY (支付
| SMS (安全
| NTF (消息通知
| MOD (内容审核
| CSC (客服工单
| MKT (营销优惠
| PIM (积分会员

**核心依赖解读

1. UAM 是几乎所有服务的强依赖（用户身份是基础）/ UAM is a strong dependency for almost all services (user identity is fundamental)
2. PAY 依赖 UAM 和 SMS（支付必须知道谁付、是否安全）/ PAY depends on UAM and SMS (payment must know who pays and if it's secure)
3. MKT 和 PIM 互相强依赖（积分和优惠通常联动）/ MKT and PIM have strong mutual dependency (points and promotions usually linked)
4. GMG 依赖多个服务（增长是综合能力体现）/ GMG depends on multiple services (growth is a comprehensive capability)

### L6-005：技术实现建议

**【自建 vs SaaS选型

**建议自建（复用价值高+数据敏感）/ Recommended for self-build (high reuse value + data sensitive)：**
- UAM/PAY/SMS（数据必须自主可控
- MKT/PIM/GMG（业务核心know-how
- CFG（深度集成开关
- DAT（数据资产

**可选SaaS（标准化程度高+接入成本低）/ Optional SaaS (high standardization + low integration cost)：**
- NTF（短信通道可采购阿里云/腾讯云
- MOD（内容审核可采购网易/数美
- MED（媒体处理可采购阿里云视频云
- CDN（可采购阿里云CDN/腾讯云CDN
- CSC（可采购Zendesk/Udesk

**【技术栈建议

- 后端框架
- 数据库
- 消息队列
- 缓存
- 搜索
- 文件存储
- 实时计算
- 报表

